Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:07.59,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,This is how it's done... sucking a dick, I mean. Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:26.20,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I wanted to be able to show Nishiro my feelings, so I studied hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.47,0:00:48.72,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:55.05,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I can do it, Nishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:33.07,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I love you, Nishiro, I really love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:36.36,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Nishiro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:38.54,Default,Kazamidori,0,0,0,,It'll be all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:43.46,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Those were the first words that person spoke to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:45.34,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Such a short phrase...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:49.08,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,That was the start of my happiest times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:02.38,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Lying painfully in a hard bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:04.84,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,I understood everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:08.34,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,The next time I opened my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:13.04,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,I realized that something had been eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:22.51,Default,Kazamidori,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. If I had been there a little sooner...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:26.49,Default,Kazamidori,0,0,0,,but half of your soul was taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:29.76,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Who... am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:33.91,Default,Kazamidori,0,0,0,,Your memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:42.39,Default,Kazamidori,0,0,0,,...It could be that you've lost your memories because that is what you wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:49.01,Default,Kazamidori,0,0,0,,My name is Kazamidori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:51.65,Default,Kazamidori,0,0,0,,You are Nishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:56.02,Default,Kazamidori,0,0,0,,Your soul that was stolen is still not lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:59.85,Default,Kazamidori,0,0,0,,Your soul and your memories - I'll definitely return them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:04.15,Default,Kazamidori,0,0,0,,Because that thing will definitely appear before you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:08.36,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,She kept her promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:13.94,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,After that she was always with me, and taught me a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:21.00,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,She was my everything. She filled the missing part of my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:24.51,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,It was a carefree and happy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:30.68,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,But when that spirit appeared for a second time, she died protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:39.14,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,I'm Tsuina Nishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:40.78,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:53.88,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Impossible. It can't be her. She died right before my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:12.18,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You don't understand the material, right? Want to review my notes? {Changing the entire meaning let's go!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:19.48,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,It's boring by yourself, right? Shall I introduce you? I know boys too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:28.86,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Hey, we'll show you around. That's important, right? Think about your student life from here on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:34.11,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,What are you spacing out about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:34.96,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.74,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,What, were you remembering something painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:38.51,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Just normal stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:46.02,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Hey, I bet it's that he had someone special before he moved! That's totally it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:47.25,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.42,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Let's go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:50.55,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Why are you dodging the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:54.30,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,If you go down a dark path, you're gonna get hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:58.50,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,It wasn't that dark of a path, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:05.36,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I'll hang out with you again when I don't have club activities. Cya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:09.82,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,What'll we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:10.74,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:15.87,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You know, you haven't asked me a single question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:20.62,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Not even my name! Are you not interested in me at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:25.91,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Hey, spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:26.87,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Yuki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:30.57,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,It is Yuki, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:35.01,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Yeah... Yuinahama Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:37.26,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,What, is there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:42.27,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I'll say this now, but it's pointless to ask with that kind of attitude! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:49.89,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,My heart is telling me that you and I have to have something together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:51.23,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,...Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:59.62,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Wait, not like that! By "something" I don't mean a kiss or whatever! I didn't mean anything perverted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:06.12,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Do you really not feel anything here? Not at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:09.63,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Fine, whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:30.44,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,What are those? Monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:33.49,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,You can see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:35.86,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I can see them, but what...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:39.32,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:45.79,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Yuki can see the Kotowari?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:15.57,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,No way! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:17.59,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,a {reishin}Drive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:22.45,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Kotowari are fragments of souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:26.00,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,They're only visible to the very spectre that broke that soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:30.63,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Someone with a damaged soul or someone who has a strong connection to them is the only exception, like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:35.38,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,What was that back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:37.01,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Have you heard of "Kotowari"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:41.11,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,What do you mean? Is that a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:43.72,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Did you think those were ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:50.23,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I live at a Shinto shrine... maybe that's why I can see ghosts and that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:59.05,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Nishiro. See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.28,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.54,Default,Obaasan,0,0,0,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:09.37,Default,Obaasan,0,0,0,,What do you mean by showing your face in front of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:12.29,Default,Obaasan,0,0,0,,Keep this kind of thing outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:16.09,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Please wait! There's something I want to ask of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:18.05,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Grandmother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:22.51,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,That Drive was handed down through Yuki's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:27.45,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,She inherited it from her real grandmother who took care of her in her childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:31.06,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,She didn't remember her grandmother at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:34.55,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,That was Yuki's explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:41.84,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Just as I was recalling Kazamidori's name, I knew that place was connected to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:48.08,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Yuki? No... I just parted ways with her a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:56.21,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Kazamidori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.46,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Kazamidori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:01.55,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,She couldn't be here. She died!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:03.55,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,I saw it myself, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:16.30,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,Stop! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:24.07,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,Please don't take this power away from me! This is all I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:26.56,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,I'll have nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:32.08,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,I need this power! I have to be able to use it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:38.09,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,It's no good, mister! You can't reach your wife or your mother like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:42.34,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,With the Drive's power, Yuki can reach this man's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:44.84,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,I don't know what she saw there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:48.47,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,Do it! Attack them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:02.90,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Geez... that was close, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:04.47,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Who... who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:08.89,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Hello there. Lovely sky tonight, isn't it? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:14.08,Default,Man,0,0,0,,That gentleman was bothering you two, right?  We saw that and had to step in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.87,0:11:19.59,Default,Miko,0,0,0,,Are you safe, Miss Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:23.25,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You're... from grandmother's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:26.22,Default,Miko,0,0,0,,Please leave the disposal to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:41.20,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,That person just wanted to be recognized...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:44.99,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,But, nobody would notice him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:50.74,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I can understand that. To say that he was bad because he made a mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:55.20,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,The person behind all that was my grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:13.34,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Nishiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:28.95,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,No. That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:30.90,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,a Kotowari!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:35.28,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:40.42,Default,Kazamidori,0,0,0,,Tsuina Nishiro. It's because of you that I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:44.67,Default,Kazamidori,0,0,0,,I was devoured by a disgusting thing that came from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.60,Default,Kazamidori,0,0,0,,It'd be better if you died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.51,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Damn... Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:06.07,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,How can you do something so awful? Hurting Nishiro like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:08.11,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:11.62,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Answer me, grandmother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.37,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:18.62,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Nishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:29.79,Default,Kotowari,0,0,0,,The Shards Torn From Your Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:36.60,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,I'm starting to want to try too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:40.31,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,You two are always clinging to each other, I've been wondering how far it'd go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:45.82,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Anyway, make sure you're living out your youth properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:48.82,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I wonder if we made her worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:52.20,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,You talk to Kiyomi about a lot of things, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:58.62,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,We talk about pretty much everything. I was wondering if I'd worried you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.71,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:03.85,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I still have that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:08.38,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,It's dark, and I hear a baby crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.38,0:14:11.72,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,It's fine. Don't worry about it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:19.60,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,It'd be nice if you would always stay by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:25.10,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I feel better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:28.14,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:33.11,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Just talking to you makes me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:36.37,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,So... please stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:46.25,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Now I think I feel even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:47.00,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:06.19,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,How did Tsuki die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:08.27,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,She was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:09.65,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Grandmother was... ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:27.50,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,What is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:34.67,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,Tsuki was protecting this bug, coddling and sheltering this meek thing who met Yuki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:40.02,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,The fact that this thing and Yuki are both here itself is like fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:43.43,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,Until this bug was here you could see Kotowari.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:48.10,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,But, Yuki, this bug can see Tsuki right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:53.11,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,The soul that Tsuki gave him too was given for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:58.53,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,In order to repair the piece of soul he lost, she used her own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:02.25,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Kazamidori's soul is inside of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:07.75,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Then, the fact that she couldn't fight fully was because I had part of her soul...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:12.75,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,And her soul is inside of Yuki, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:18.59,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,This bug's heart was transplanted when you were a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:20.94,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,It's Tsuki's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:26.20,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,That day when Nishiro arrived, I felt something in my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:29.81,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,If that was the thoughts... of my grandmother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:31.40,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Stop already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:34.05,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,You've probably noticed, right, you bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.57,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,You're the one who killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:42.83,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,The reason that left hand can move is because the part of your soul that was fractured is living somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:47.40,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,After all, Kotowari are pieces of damaged souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.58,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,So then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:55.46,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,the piece of Nishiro's soul is living inside of that spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:17:00.97,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,No! The only people who can see a Kotowari is the person who lost a piece of their soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:03.85,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,So what does that make that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.14,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:07.35,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,my Kotowari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:09.14,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,That thing was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:24.99,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,Things have gotten strained between you and Yuki, right? She's really clammed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:30.54,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,It's not like you fought or anything, right? Yuki is still really worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:37.05,Default,Kiyomi,0,0,0,,We're meeting up today, so take a bath and get over there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:05.61,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,I can't forgive myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:10.56,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,I caused Kazamidori to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:17.25,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Both of us are here because of my grandmother's own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.92,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,That's true, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:24.68,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You said you can't forgive yourself, but I'm the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:30.68,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Because the fact that I can feel this happiness is because of my grandmother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:04.55,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,I can't think about anything but being together with you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:02.61,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:08.04,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Nishiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:35.67,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Why... why would you appear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:37.39,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,You're part of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:39.45,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Why did you kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.45,0:20:42.15,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Why did you kill her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:45.11,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:47.95,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,But even if I try and will you to do something, it's useless?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:52.00,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,In that case... I don't need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:02.58,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Just disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:17.43,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,You insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.43,0:21:22.94,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,Even with this left hand, do you think you can kill that Kotowari?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:24.59,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:31.30,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,This is a letter that Tsuki sent with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:35.70,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,Your past is all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:42.21,Default,Tsuki,0,0,0,,As we discussed previously, I was able to make contact with the child who is responsible for the Kotowari.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:46.74,Default,Tsuki,0,0,0,,He was taken in from his parents by an old woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:49.21,Default,Tsuki,0,0,0,,The old woman was withdrawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:53.76,Default,Tsuki,0,0,0,,She cannot move her hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:22:10.07,Default,Tsuki,0,0,0,,She thought to take care of the boy and use him to repair her hands.{check - soo long...}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:23.27,Default,Tsuki,0,0,0,,I understand the true form of the boy's Kotowari. It's the awareness of his sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:30.00,Default,Tsuki,0,0,0,,The woman who took care of him had him take the souls himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.00,0:22:35.56,Default,Tsuki,0,0,0,,He could feel the lives and pull them into his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:41.31,Default,Tsuki,0,0,0,,I tried to ask her to stop repeatedly, but the old woman would not listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:45.52,Default,Tsuki,0,0,0,,I knew this could only come to grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.52,0:22:53.70,Default,Tsuki,0,0,0,,The boy's despair continued, and so he cast away the memories of these souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.09,0:22:59.31,Default,Tsuki,0,0,0,,which lead to something truly frightful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:06.97,Default,Tsuki,0,0,0,,From the bottom of my heart, I hope that I can cleanse this boy's sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:14.80,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,What should I do? Kazamidori...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.60,0:23:23.81,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Kazamidori! I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:25.86,Default,Kazamidori,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.81,0:23:31.15,Default,Grandmother,0,0,0,,You better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.54,0:23:45.41,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Kazamidori!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.41,0:23:47.14,Default,Kazamidori,0,0,0,,Quickly, this girl-!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.22,0:23:55.47,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Kazamidori!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.24,0:24:26.91,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't fight just out of hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.40,0:24:35.87,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Don't waste what my grandmother did. That child...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.87,0:24:40.84,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,that child is a piece of a soul. Nishiro, you're the only one who can stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.18,0:24:43.36,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,I have to stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.69,0:24:55.52,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Is it different somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.11,0:25:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandmother's Kotowari was attacked by that child because she attacked its tummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.16,0:25:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,To get me back...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.39,0:25:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Weakness...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.58,0:25:12.05,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I'll restrain it! I'm counting on you, Nishiro!{Well, didn't make any sense here}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.29,0:25:25.60,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Don't you hurt Yuki! Don't take anything else from me-!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.64,0:25:28.48,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.69,0:25:32.08,Default,Young Nishiro,0,0,0,,I'm asking you, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.54,0:25:35.74,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Nishiro...?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.74,0:25:37.89,Default,Young Nishiro,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.40,0:25:45.16,Default,Young Nishiro,0,0,0,,I stole away many lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.91,0:25:48.54,Default,Young Nishiro,0,0,0,,Somehow, I can't seem to care.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.54,0:25:51.54,Default,Young Nishiro,0,0,0,,So, I'm asking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.02,0:25:55.29,Default,Young Nishiro,0,0,0,,What's left in these hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.29,0:25:58.80,Default,Young Nishiro,0,0,0,,the feeling of those poor souls...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.38,0:26:03.24,Default,Young Nishiro,0,0,0,,Please let them go to their mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.81,0:26:10.56,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,You were always protecting them, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.56,0:26:15.77,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,The many lives that couldn't be born...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.77,0:26:20.28,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,The precious heart of the kind person I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.28,0:26:26.28,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Were you saying this from the beginning? I'll forgive these sins and live properly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.18,0:26:35.02,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Because... your sins are mine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.02,0:26:36.68,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.26,0:26:51.54,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.54,0:26:53.49,Default,Nishiro,0,0,0,,Hey, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.22,0:27:44.99,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,Nishiro... Nishiro! Ah, I... I'm gonna-!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.38,0:28:10.98,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,That spot really does get me going.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.98,0:28:14.68,Default,Yuki,0,0,0,,I can't help it with you, Nishiro!